// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Contact Name : A Strange Mystical Trinket 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P1471094079" "A Strange Mystical Trinket"
// LocationString :
"P1934614585" "Alignment Mission"
// ProfessionString :
"P856364347" ""
// AskAboutTextOverride :
"P800262832" "Reconsider your options."
// ContactRequiresText :
"P3611273721" "You are of the wrong alignment to get this tip."
// IDontKnowYouString :
"P71529226" "You're unsure of exactly what to do with this information."
// NoTasksRemainingString :
"P3469732091" "This tip is of no use to you."
// PlayerBusyString :
"P1640634726" "You already have enough tips to act on at this time."
// ComeBackLaterString :
"P3623388284" "You're currently too busy to act upon this information."
// FailsafeLevelString :
"P3299591369" "Failsafe"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P2126696074" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Strange Mystical Trinket</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You discover a strange mystical trinket that looks dangerous and fascinating at the same time.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Examine the trinket, something about it is familiar. </scale></font></color><br><br><br><br>This bizarre mystical trinket looks like a cross between a brooch and an offering plate. It is made of unique and unidentifiable materials, crafted in an unfamiliar style and covered with strange symbols. In fact, it is so unique that you've only seen one thing similar to this design... the signature artifact of Kel'Morgath, a powerful wizard of the Circle of Thorns! If Kel'Morgath is without his artifact then he will be weakened. If this is a copy then perhaps you can match or counter his power and strike against him! Either way you will need to move quickly and discover Kel'Morgath's lair within the mysterious city of Oranbega before he can rectify this chink in his defenses."
// Answer Text :
"P835531080" "VILLAIN: Strike against Kel'Morgath while he's weak!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
"P3375353421" "Now is not a good time to investigate this tip.  Wait until you are within the streets of The Rogue Isles before you attempt any investigation."
// Answer Text :
"P385518726" "Investigate this tip later"
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


