// Contact Name : A Tattered Flyer 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P842665984" "A Tattered Flyer"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P2813734945" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Tattered Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find a torn and trampled flyer on the street announcing that Beautiful Annabella's Carnival is going to be in Paragon City holding a month of fun for the whole family. Annabella may be beautiful, but her heart and soul are twisted and evil to the core.  She just got out of the Zig, legitimately, but everyone knows that the system doesn't work.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Whatever her little family fun carnival is on the surface, it is certainly hiding an insidious plot underneath. You don't have proof... yet, but you do have a plan to get it.</scale></font></color><br><br>  It's no big secret that Annabella's achilles heel is her love for her favorite Strongman, aptly named Achilles. Putting the hurt on him will force her to admit to her evil machinations, because if she doesn't, then you'll show her just how mortal Achilles really is!"
// Answer Text :
"P177521606" "VILLAIN: Pain separates the truth from lies. A lover's cry is pain unequaled."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


