// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Contact Name : Proper Documents 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Name :
"P1966061608" "Proper Documents"
// LocationString :
// ProfessionString :
// AskAboutTextOverride :
// ContactRequiresText :
// IDontKnowYouString :
// NoTasksRemainingString :
// PlayerBusyString :
// ComeBackLaterString :
// FailsafeLevelString :

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page VigilanteToVillain Text :
"P181812891" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Proper Documents</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You had to read the legal documents over a few times, and you even gave the City Representative a second glance to make sure she wasn't an automaton, but everything looks legit. The Nemesis Army is throwing a parade this Sunday. This can only end in tears.<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>PREPARE YOURSELF... FOR BRASS SUNDAY... Sunday... sunday!</scale></font></color><br><br>Ok... the flyers were annoying, but the bullhorns are little much. This is just ridiculous. Everyone is talking about the big parade that the Nemesis Army is preparing to unleash upon Paragon City, and everyone is angry about it. Freedom of Assembly your butt... Nemesis is up to something, and everyone knows it! While the heroes of the city theorize over what his real agenda is, you know that the time to strike is now. No matter how peaceful they may seem at the moment, they are still the enemy."
// Answer Text :
"P1147636906" "VILLAIN: I won't let you get away with this, Nemesis!"
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


